quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,115,"Ṣé ẹ lérò pé A kàn ṣẹ̀dá yín fún ìranù ni, àti pé dájúdájú wọn ò níí da yín padà sọ́dọ̀ Wa?”"
  23,116,"Nítorí náà, Allāhu Ọba Òdodo ga. Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun, Olúwa Ìtẹ́ alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé."
  23,117,"Ẹni tí ó bá pe ọlọ́hun mìíràn pẹ̀lú Allāhu, kò ní ẹ̀rí lọ́wọ́ lórí rẹ̀. Dájúdájú ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ rẹ̀ sì wà lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ kò níí jèrè."
  25,61,"Ìbùkún ni fún Ẹni tí Ó ṣe àwọn ibùsọ̀ ìràwọ̀ sínú sánmọ̀. Ó tún ṣe òòrùn àti òṣùpá ní ìmọ́lẹ̀ sínú rẹ̀."
  25,62,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó ṣe òru àti ọ̀sán ní ìtẹ̀léǹtẹ̀lé (tí ìkíní yàtọ̀ sí ìkejì) nítorí ẹni tí ó bá gbèrò láti ṣe ìrántí (Allāhu) tàbí tí ó bá gbèrò ìdúpẹ́ (fún Un)."
  25,63,"Àwọn ẹrúsìn Àjọkẹ́-ayé ni àwọn tó ń rìn jẹ́ẹ́jẹ́ lórí ilẹ̀. Nígbà tí àwọn òpè bá sì dojú ọ̀rọ̀ kọ wọ́n, wọn yóò sọ ọ̀rọ̀ àlàáfíà."
  26,34,"(Fir‘aon) wí fún àwọn ìjòyè tí wọ́n wà ní àyíká rẹ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú èyí ni onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa."
  26,35,"Ó fẹ́ ko yín kúrò lórí ilẹ̀ yín ni. Kí ni ohun tí ẹ máa mú wá ní ìmọ̀ràn?”1 {1}",1:[Nínú sūrah Al-’a‘rọ̄f;  7:109-110, gbólóhùn “Dájúdájú èyí ni onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa. Ó fẹ́ ko yín kúrò lórí ilẹ̀ yín ni.”, ó jáde láti ẹnu àwọn ìjòyè Fir‘aon. Àmọ́ nínú sūrah yìí, sūrah aṣ-Ṣu‘arọ̄’; 26:34-35, gbólóhùn yẹn jáde láti ẹnu Fir‘aon. Ìtúmọ̀ èyí ni pé, Fir‘aon sọ gbólóhùn náà, àwọn ìjòyè rẹ̀ náà gbè é lẹ́sẹ̀. Ọ̀rọ̀ náà sì di àgbàsọ láààrin ara wọn.]
  26,36,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Dá òun àti arákùnrin rẹ̀ dúró ná, kí o sì rán àwọn akónijọsí àwọn ìlú {1}",1:[Àwọn akójijọ ni àwọn alukoro rẹ̀, àwọn aláago atótó-arére.]
  27,7,"(Rántí) nígbà tí (Ànábì) Mūsā sọ fún àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú mo rí iná kan. Mo sì máa lọ mú ìró kan wá fún yín láti ibẹ̀, tàbí kí n̄g mú ògúnná kan tó ń tanná wá fún yín nítorí kí ẹ lè yẹ́ná."
  27,8,"Nígbà tí ó dé ibẹ̀, A pèpè pé kí ìbùkún máa bẹ fún ẹni tí ó wà níbi iná náà àti ẹni tí ó wà ní àyíká rẹ̀. Mímọ́ sì ni fún Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  27,9,"Mūsā, dájúdájú (ẹni tí ó ń bá ọ sọ̀rọ̀), Èmi ni Allāhu, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."